# Meta provider (jumon-mcp)

## Platform id

`meta` — gateway provider segment and `explore_platform` platform name.

## P0

- Package wired in `wire.go`; `RegisterTools` registers **zero** tools until P1.
- `proxy.go` — all calls via `gateway.Client` (`platformName = "meta"`).

## Tool naming (P1+)

Prefix `meta_`. Ad account ids: `act_` prefix.

## API version

Document **v25.0** in schemas/descriptions. Authoritative version in mcp-ads-manager `META_GRAPH_API_VERSION`.

## Insights

Meta covers Facebook, Instagram, and other placements. Guide agents to Insights `breakdowns` (e.g. `publisher_platform`) — not separate platforms.

## Do not

- Call Graph API directly from Go.
- Store tokens in this repo.
